WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:04.880
Well, good evening everybody. Thank you

00:00:02.399 --> 00:00:09.120
for joining us again tonight. I got

00:00:04.880 --> 00:00:12.559
this today that will get rid

00:00:09.120 --> 00:00:14.239
of every fly. Somebody sent this

00:00:12.559 --> 00:00:15.920
to me; I thought that was the coolest

00:00:14.240 --> 00:00:18.000
thing ever. I told Diana I said, "Guess

00:00:15.920 --> 00:00:19.759
what? I'm the Terminator."So,

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:23.279
we're going to go after the flies

00:00:19.760 --> 00:00:24.960
today. If there's a fly, he's dead. So,

00:00:23.279 --> 00:00:26.800
I'm excited about it. I loaded it with

00:00:24.960 --> 00:00:29.199
the salt from the Himalaya and Himalayan

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:30.960
salt crystals. I can see it go,

00:00:29.199 --> 00:00:33.200
and so it's fun to play with.

00:00:30.960 --> 00:00:35.600
I've been shooting at flies all the

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:37.520
time. You know, I shot myself with it;

00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:39.040
it stings really bad. But I thought,

00:00:37.520 --> 00:00:40.480
yeah, that was fun. So, whoever sent

00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:43.360
that, I appreciate that. That was

00:00:40.480 --> 00:00:45.440
kind of you. So, we don't have fly

00:00:43.360 --> 00:00:46.800
problems no more. In fact, I've been

00:00:45.440 --> 00:00:48.470
looking for flies. I said, leave the

00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:50.320
door open.

00:00:50.320 --> 00:00:56.960
Leave the door open. Let's do this.

00:00:53.680 --> 00:01:00.239
All right. Well, last night was

00:00:56.960 --> 00:01:04.239
different. You know, I've prayed

00:01:00.239 --> 00:01:07.280
about that all day today. What I saw

00:01:04.239 --> 00:01:08.960
about the person in the boat, Diana

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:10.640
and I, we discussed it. We had to run

00:01:08.960 --> 00:01:12.479
errands and do some things, and I

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:14.960
told her, we were talking, she went through

00:01:12.479 --> 00:01:16.880
all the visions and things the Lord has

00:01:14.960 --> 00:01:18.158
been showing me. She asked me about

00:01:16.880 --> 00:01:20.640
certain things today. It was interesting

00:01:18.159 --> 00:01:24.320
because Diana doesn't usually ever do that.

00:01:20.640 --> 00:01:27.200
But she said, "As Joseph saw seven fat

00:01:24.320 --> 00:01:30.960
cows and seven skinny cows, did it have

00:01:27.200 --> 00:01:34.799
anything to do with a cow?"The

00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:38.559
cow represented seven plentiful

00:01:34.799 --> 00:01:40.479
years and seven bad years.

00:01:38.560 --> 00:01:44.400
It was the Lord talking

00:01:40.479 --> 00:01:46.640
about two shmita cycles.

00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:50.000
It started with two shmita cycles,

00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:53.040
two seven-year periods.

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:56.720
That's the point I say, because I

00:01:54.640 --> 00:01:57.920
was the reason why I brought it up. I've

00:01:56.720 --> 00:02:00.000
been thinking and meditating on the

00:01:57.920 --> 00:02:02.399
visions the Lord shows me, that I saw a

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:04.880
girl in a boat

00:02:02.399 --> 00:02:07.920
and she was in the Caribbean.

00:02:04.880 --> 00:02:10.799
It was a white woman and she was on a

00:02:07.920 --> 00:02:13.440
boat that the sail was messed up and she

00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:16.080
was sailing for fun.

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:18.480
I could see her last night bobbing

00:02:16.080 --> 00:02:21.120
up and down in the water as a storm on

00:02:18.480 --> 00:02:23.599
the sea was happening. She was

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:25.680
bobbing up and down and she was crying

00:02:23.599 --> 00:02:29.519
and she was sitting on the

00:02:25.680 --> 00:02:31.920
deck of this

00:02:29.520 --> 00:02:33.760
white boat and it was moving up and

00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:36.000
down; she was

00:02:33.760 --> 00:02:37.920
sobbing because she had no way of

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:41.560
communicating to people to tell them that

00:02:37.920 --> 00:02:41.559
she was in distress

00:02:41.680 --> 00:02:45.840
and she was too far out for the Coast

00:02:43.519 --> 00:02:48.319
Guard to hear her or for them to be

00:02:45.840 --> 00:02:50.160
watching for her. She was too far out.

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:52.238
But she came from Florida. There was

00:02:50.160 --> 00:02:54.640
something about her in the

00:02:52.239 --> 00:02:57.360
Caribbean that she got into;

00:02:54.640 --> 00:02:59.359
something happened and I was interceding

00:02:57.360 --> 00:03:01.200
for this. I was thinking is this a

00:02:59.360 --> 00:03:04.400
metaphor?

00:03:01.200 --> 00:03:06.480
As I was praying into

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:08.400
that, I was seeing people behind

00:03:06.480 --> 00:03:11.760
their computers last night and they were

00:03:08.400 --> 00:03:13.920
saying, "Does God really care about me?

00:03:11.760 --> 00:03:16.079
I feel all alone.

00:03:13.920 --> 00:03:20.319
I have no family. I

00:03:16.080 --> 00:03:22.879
come, I work 8 to 5,

00:03:20.319 --> 00:03:24.720
I'm by myself all the time,"and they

00:03:22.879 --> 00:03:26.879
were thinking about harming themselves

00:03:24.720 --> 00:03:29.599
physically. They were feeling that they

00:03:26.879 --> 00:03:34.000
were completely lost.

00:03:29.599 --> 00:03:37.280
Does God really care about me? Does

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:40.000
God really understand that I'm

00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:42.319
hurting right now? Does he even care

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:45.200
that I am?

00:03:42.319 --> 00:03:48.000
And as I was praying, I could feel the

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:50.159
hopelessness of these individuals last

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:53.360
night, that they felt like there was no

00:03:50.159 --> 00:03:57.679
hope for their life. There was such a

00:03:53.360 --> 00:04:02.640
depression and such a sense of not

00:03:57.680 --> 00:04:06.239
self-worth, so inadequate.

00:04:02.640 --> 00:04:09.359
It was so heavy. And as I was praying, I

00:04:06.239 --> 00:04:12.400
saw a cork bobbing down in the water and

00:04:09.360 --> 00:04:15.280
then it became a person.

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:17.120
And as they began to sink into the water

00:04:15.280 --> 00:04:19.600
and the water was about to take their

00:04:17.120 --> 00:04:22.079
last breath

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:24.240
in their life, they would shoot up to

00:04:22.079 --> 00:04:26.720
the top and they would get just enough

00:04:24.240 --> 00:04:28.560
air just to sustain them to keep their

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:30.400
body alive. Almost like the bread of

00:04:28.560 --> 00:04:32.240
affliction.

00:04:30.400 --> 00:04:33.919
And I could see them dropping back down

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:35.759
and trying to fight to come up to the

00:04:33.919 --> 00:04:37.520
air again. And they were fighting for

00:04:35.759 --> 00:04:40.639
everything they had to have just one

00:04:37.520 --> 00:04:43.919
more breath of air.

00:04:40.639 --> 00:04:46.960
And that's the way they were living.

00:04:43.919 --> 00:04:49.198
If I could just get one more breath of

00:04:46.960 --> 00:04:52.560
air. And they go, [gasps]

00:04:49.199 --> 00:04:56.160
and they go back down.

00:04:52.560 --> 00:04:58.960
And it was very heavy.

00:04:56.160 --> 00:05:00.479
As I'm saying this, it's heavy.

00:04:58.960 --> 00:05:03.840
But I went over the visions and I

00:05:00.479 --> 00:05:06.080
thought, is this girl in the ocean, is

00:05:03.840 --> 00:05:08.400
this a type of shadow of where

00:05:06.080 --> 00:05:10.159
people are spiritually,

00:05:08.400 --> 00:05:13.520
of where they are with their

00:05:10.160 --> 00:05:15.600
relationship with the Lord?

00:05:13.520 --> 00:05:18.000
That God is wanting you to come out of

00:05:15.600 --> 00:05:21.360
the barely getting by, the survival

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:23.840
stage, and come into thriving.

00:05:21.360 --> 00:05:25.840
He wants you to thrive the rest. He

00:05:23.840 --> 00:05:27.679
wants you to be the head and not the

00:05:25.840 --> 00:05:30.479
tail. Above and not beneath. Go through

00:05:27.680 --> 00:05:32.560
and not go under. To have that

00:05:30.479 --> 00:05:35.599
relationship with him that you say,

00:05:32.560 --> 00:05:37.360
"Hello, Father. How are you doing

00:05:35.600 --> 00:05:39.520
today?"That

00:05:39.520 --> 00:05:43.840
you become intimate with God. When

00:05:41.759 --> 00:05:46.560
you get real with God, I say it all the

00:05:43.840 --> 00:05:48.799
time. When you get real with God, God

00:05:46.560 --> 00:05:50.160
will become real to you. Stop being

00:05:48.800 --> 00:05:53.199
fake.

00:05:50.160 --> 00:05:54.639
I went over all the major ministries,

00:05:53.199 --> 00:05:56.639
all the people that I've talked to on

00:05:54.639 --> 00:05:59.759
the phone that I used to dream to talk

00:05:56.639 --> 00:06:02.720
to, and you realize how human they truly

00:05:59.759 --> 00:06:05.840
are. That they are just a vessel that

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:08.160
said yes, just like me.

00:06:05.840 --> 00:06:10.719
And how I have strategically done

00:06:08.160 --> 00:06:12.639
everything the Lord has told me to do to

00:06:10.720 --> 00:06:14.880
get to where I'm at right now and where

00:06:12.639 --> 00:06:17.039
he tells me I'm going.

00:06:14.880 --> 00:06:19.360
And how I don't ever want the pressure

00:06:17.039 --> 00:06:22.080
of this to ever choke out the

00:06:19.360 --> 00:06:24.319
relationship that I have with him. It's

00:06:22.080 --> 00:06:26.318
more valuable than anything else.

00:06:24.319 --> 00:06:27.840
It's like I

00:06:26.319 --> 00:06:29.680
told one minister, I don't care about

00:06:27.840 --> 00:06:31.119
the White House. I don't care about

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:33.840
certain

00:06:31.120 --> 00:06:35.440
stuff. In fact, I think it's a joke. I

00:06:33.840 --> 00:06:38.080
talk to the King of Kings and I see

00:06:35.440 --> 00:06:41.600
angels. They come and visit. That's the

00:06:38.080 --> 00:06:45.039
thing to me. Sitting at the dryer and

00:06:41.600 --> 00:06:46.560
losing yourself with prayer, and that's

00:06:45.039 --> 00:06:48.639
what I did. Folding laundry, helping

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:51.680
Diana, doing things like that, seeking

00:06:48.639 --> 00:06:53.840
him and finding him.

00:06:51.680 --> 00:06:57.520
All this other—I want to call it crap.

00:06:53.840 --> 00:07:00.159
Sorry, but it is, the spiritual stuff, all the

00:06:57.520 --> 00:07:02.799
requests,

00:07:00.160 --> 00:07:05.919
all that, it's crap. It's a distraction.

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:07.680
I talked to people across this

00:07:05.919 --> 00:07:10.560
camera because the Lord

00:07:07.680 --> 00:07:12.319
told me to. But I thought about it a lot

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:14.800
today. I thought about the pressure of

00:07:12.319 --> 00:07:18.639
ministry. I have some ministers, I talk

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:22.560
to them. They got 40 and 50 staff, 250

00:07:18.639 --> 00:07:25.440
staff. They got huge overhead.

00:07:22.560 --> 00:07:26.720
They got huge bills, huge. And if they

00:07:25.440 --> 00:07:28.400
don't have a certain amount of money

00:07:26.720 --> 00:07:30.800
come in through their ministry, they're

00:07:28.400 --> 00:07:33.440
in trouble. So they push books. They

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:35.680
push things. And I'm not criticizing.

00:07:33.440 --> 00:07:38.639
That's just not where

00:07:35.680 --> 00:07:40.639
my heart is. I just want to be Brandon. I

00:07:38.639 --> 00:07:42.240
don't want the pressure of all that with

00:07:40.639 --> 00:07:44.319
having families and being

00:07:42.240 --> 00:07:46.319
responsible. You got to make sure

00:07:44.319 --> 00:07:48.240
they got their bills paid by your

00:07:46.319 --> 00:07:49.919
ministry paying their salary and you got

00:07:48.240 --> 00:07:52.880
all that. And I go, "Good Lord."And

00:07:49.919 --> 00:07:56.639
Diana goes, "Brandon, do you see we

00:07:52.880 --> 00:07:58.479
can say whatever I want to say?"And

00:07:56.639 --> 00:08:02.080
they look at me as a wild

00:07:58.479 --> 00:08:04.960
hair. I say what he says, but I

00:08:02.080 --> 00:08:08.240
have no fear of it. Last night I told

00:08:04.960 --> 00:08:10.638
you I saw the Colombian president, his

00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:12.000
buddies in a box being shipped to him.

00:08:10.639 --> 00:08:12.560
And after it was over—Colombia.

00:08:12.000 --> 00:08:17.039
Colombia,

00:08:12.560 --> 00:08:19.919
sorry. Thank you, son.

00:08:17.039 --> 00:08:21.680
Rewind that. Colombia. But I saw his

00:08:19.919 --> 00:08:23.039
buddies in a box and the Lord said,

00:08:21.680 --> 00:08:24.400
"Anoint your place of the Lord."I saw a

00:08:23.039 --> 00:08:26.318
witch after him. I saw that. But I

00:08:24.400 --> 00:08:28.799
didn't have no fear saying it. And most

00:08:26.319 --> 00:08:30.160
people go, "My god, we got the emails.

00:08:28.800 --> 00:08:31.280
Are you kidding me? Do you say all that?"I

00:08:30.160 --> 00:08:33.680
said, "I have nothing to fear

00:08:31.280 --> 00:08:35.679
because I have nothing to lose."If

00:08:33.679 --> 00:08:37.598
we still do our business and

00:08:35.679 --> 00:08:39.760
do things on the side there, if this

00:08:37.599 --> 00:08:41.919
gets turned off, I truly mean that. I

00:08:39.760 --> 00:08:44.240
did this all for the Lord. There's

00:08:41.919 --> 00:08:46.480
nothing behind it other than I am sold

00:08:44.240 --> 00:08:49.200
out to Jesus.

00:08:46.480 --> 00:08:50.720
And I told them and I think

00:08:49.200 --> 00:08:52.480
that's probably why a lot of these other

00:08:50.720 --> 00:08:54.080
ministries, big ministries, they

00:08:52.480 --> 00:08:55.680
hold me at arms distance because they

00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:57.279
don't know what I'm going to do. And

00:08:55.680 --> 00:09:00.000
that's the truth. I don't know what I'm

00:08:57.279 --> 00:09:02.480
going to do. I'm free.

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:04.640
I say what he says to say. And if

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:06.000
there's repercussions behind it, I pay

00:09:04.640 --> 00:09:07.920
the price for I say, "Lord, this is what

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:10.160
you told me to do."If the channel gets

00:09:07.920 --> 00:09:13.519
turned off, they silenced me

00:09:10.160 --> 00:09:14.959
last night again. Then everybody had

00:09:13.519 --> 00:09:16.959
to go, 'Hey, we can't hear you anymore.'YouTube

00:09:14.959 --> 00:09:18.959
got ticked off, and

00:09:16.959 --> 00:09:21.279
we get these things. They say, 'You

00:09:18.959 --> 00:09:24.560
can't say that,'and they

00:09:21.279 --> 00:09:26.560
mute me.

00:09:24.560 --> 00:09:28.640
Hello, YouTube.

00:09:26.560 --> 00:09:30.479
But I'm bold as a lion, and I'll say

00:09:28.640 --> 00:09:32.560
what He says to say, and I don't care.

00:09:30.480 --> 00:09:35.200
I did the best I

00:09:32.560 --> 00:09:36.880
could, and I'll stand before Him and

00:09:35.200 --> 00:09:39.600
say, 'Lord, I gave You everything I got.'And

00:09:36.880 --> 00:09:41.920
that might mean that Diana

00:09:39.600 --> 00:09:43.680
goes, 'You have more, you know what,

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:46.319
rocks than I've ever seen anybody have

00:09:43.680 --> 00:09:48.160
in my life.'Honey, I can't

00:09:46.320 --> 00:09:50.480
believe some of the stuff you say, but I

00:09:48.160 --> 00:09:52.719
say it because I don't fear you; I fear

00:09:50.480 --> 00:09:55.600
Him.

00:09:52.720 --> 00:09:57.200
I'm sold out. I was going over

00:09:55.600 --> 00:09:59.360
the visions and going over things. I

00:09:57.200 --> 00:10:01.360
think, my God, I've said some things on

00:09:59.360 --> 00:10:02.800
the internet. They blotted me out

00:10:01.360 --> 00:10:04.720
last night, and I couldn't figure out why.

00:10:02.800 --> 00:10:07.439
Nobody could hear me.

00:10:04.720 --> 00:10:09.360
They muted me, and they wanted you to

00:10:07.440 --> 00:10:11.279
leave. They didn't want you hearing what

00:10:09.360 --> 00:10:12.800
I was saying anymore, so you had to

00:10:11.279 --> 00:10:14.959
refresh it and come back in. For a lot of you—that

00:10:12.800 --> 00:10:17.199
thousand-plus

00:10:14.959 --> 00:10:18.079
where it all

00:10:17.200 --> 00:10:20.000
dropped—so

00:10:18.079 --> 00:10:22.239
it is what it is.

00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:23.839
Everybody lost sound

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:28.240
because YouTube didn't like what I said

00:10:23.839 --> 00:10:31.360
last night. And so, am I

00:10:28.240 --> 00:10:34.399
afraid of that? Not even a little bit.

00:10:31.360 --> 00:10:39.040
I didn't get myself here;

00:10:34.399 --> 00:10:42.399
I didn't do any of it. He did it all.

00:10:39.040 --> 00:10:45.279
Everything I have—I lived in an 800-square-foot

00:10:42.399 --> 00:10:47.839
house for 17 years of my life with

00:10:45.279 --> 00:10:49.760
cockroaches and meth dealers

00:10:47.839 --> 00:10:51.440
all around me. I've been at the bottom

00:10:49.760 --> 00:10:54.319
of the barrel, and now the Lord's blessed

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:57.760
me. I look around and say,

00:10:54.320 --> 00:11:00.800
'I've had little, and

00:10:57.760 --> 00:11:02.720
I'm not moved by any of it.'I lived

00:11:00.800 --> 00:11:05.279
with nothing, barely scrimping on

00:11:02.720 --> 00:11:07.600
food stamps. You understand, when you

00:11:05.279 --> 00:11:09.439
are sold out to Him

00:11:07.600 --> 00:11:12.000
and there's nothing that you've done in

00:11:09.440 --> 00:11:14.720
your life to take credit for, you are

00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:18.320
able to be really free, because I was

00:11:14.720 --> 00:11:21.440
happy then and I'm happy now.

00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:24.160
I love the Lord, but

00:11:21.440 --> 00:11:25.760
like I said,

00:11:24.160 --> 00:11:27.920
my biggest thing is always praying with

00:11:25.760 --> 00:11:29.360
my kids, teaching them how to pray,

00:11:27.920 --> 00:11:31.439
teaching them how to deep dip in the

00:11:29.360 --> 00:11:33.360
rivers. My biggest thing is to teach

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:34.640
Paisley. I see the intercessory prayer

00:11:33.360 --> 00:11:37.120
gifts on her. The Lord told me she's

00:11:34.640 --> 00:11:38.720
going to start to see as she's seeing. There are

00:11:37.120 --> 00:11:40.240
things that I don't talk about,

00:11:38.720 --> 00:11:42.880
but my little girl is walking in the

00:11:40.240 --> 00:11:44.240
supernatural at ten years old, and she's

00:11:42.880 --> 00:11:46.000
already starting to see over and she's

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:47.839
able to do things. And I impart.

00:11:46.000 --> 00:11:49.760
I lay hands on her and

00:11:47.839 --> 00:11:50.959
I impart.

00:11:49.760 --> 00:11:53.439
I teach her how to jump in that

00:11:50.959 --> 00:11:55.279
river as a child. I do the same with

00:11:53.440 --> 00:11:57.600
Braden. And if Megan were

00:11:55.279 --> 00:12:00.079
not overcoming, I would do the same

00:11:57.600 --> 00:12:02.079
for her, but right now she's overcoming.

00:12:00.079 --> 00:12:03.599
I still pray for her

00:12:02.079 --> 00:12:04.880
all the time, but it's not like I try to

00:12:03.600 --> 00:12:07.200
say, 'Honey, will you see?'because she

00:12:04.880 --> 00:12:11.839
wouldn't tell us if she could.

00:12:07.200 --> 00:12:15.399
I'm sure she does.

00:12:11.839 --> 00:12:15.399
I'm free tonight.

00:12:15.920 --> 00:12:20.000
As it clicked today while we

00:12:18.480 --> 00:12:22.639
were going over the visions and what the

00:12:20.000 --> 00:12:24.800
Lord has done, there are

00:12:22.639 --> 00:12:26.880
things that the Lord shows me

00:12:24.800 --> 00:12:29.120
that we've prayed away. I know we've

00:12:26.880 --> 00:12:31.519
stopped things by the Spirit of God,

00:12:29.120 --> 00:12:33.600
praying for things and interceding for this

00:12:31.519 --> 00:12:35.519
man in

00:12:33.600 --> 00:12:37.519
Colombia.

00:12:35.519 --> 00:12:39.279
I said, 'Lord, I haven't had a lot

00:12:37.519 --> 00:12:40.480
of visions in the last couple of days.

00:12:39.279 --> 00:12:42.560
You haven't shown me what's going on.'He

00:12:40.480 --> 00:12:44.959
said, 'I told you when I don't

00:12:42.560 --> 00:12:47.599
show you something to pray over what

00:12:44.959 --> 00:12:49.599
I've given you. I gave you something

00:12:47.600 --> 00:12:51.600
that you just see—it's amazing—and

00:12:49.600 --> 00:12:53.760
you just cast it aside

00:12:51.600 --> 00:12:55.519
and keep marching.'He said,

00:12:53.760 --> 00:12:56.639
'It's like going at Christmas time and

00:12:55.519 --> 00:12:58.560
you're opening up gifts and you go,

00:12:56.639 --> 00:13:00.079
"Where's the next one? Where's the next one?"and

00:12:58.560 --> 00:13:04.638
you don't realize what you

00:13:00.079 --> 00:13:06.719
just unwrapped.'What did He give you?

00:13:04.639 --> 00:13:07.839
Well, hold on a minute.

00:13:06.720 --> 00:13:09.680
You're a child because you're so

00:13:07.839 --> 00:13:11.600
excited about all the stuff under the

00:13:09.680 --> 00:13:13.439
tree. He keeps giving you all this

00:13:11.600 --> 00:13:16.399
stuff and you're not looking at what He

00:13:13.440 --> 00:13:17.760
gave you out of the box.

00:13:16.399 --> 00:13:19.600
You're taking it for granted

00:13:17.760 --> 00:13:22.160
because you put it aside and forgot

00:13:19.600 --> 00:13:24.800
that you even opened it because you're

00:13:22.160 --> 00:13:26.480
looking at what's ahead. He said,

00:13:24.800 --> 00:13:28.319
'Stop looking at what's underneath the

00:13:26.480 --> 00:13:29.839
tree and look at what I already gave you

00:13:28.320 --> 00:13:33.000
to unwrap and what I'm telling you to

00:13:29.839 --> 00:13:33.000
pray

00:13:36.240 --> 00:13:40.800
over.'I'm

00:13:38.800 --> 00:13:43.599
trying to tell you to pray over the

00:13:40.800 --> 00:13:45.359
man in Colombia because he's going to lose

00:13:43.600 --> 00:13:46.800
two friends,

00:13:45.360 --> 00:13:49.440
somebody really close to him with a

00:13:46.800 --> 00:13:51.760
beard, and you can pray about this. I

00:13:49.440 --> 00:13:53.760
thought, 'Can I stop it? Are

00:13:51.760 --> 00:13:55.760
there things that You tell me to stop?'because

00:13:53.760 --> 00:13:59.040
You told me You want revival in

00:13:55.760 --> 00:14:00.720
Colombia. The ultimate thing is there's

00:13:59.040 --> 00:14:01.680
witchcraft in the nation and the Lord

00:14:00.720 --> 00:14:04.399
said, 'I'm going to deal with it. But

00:14:01.680 --> 00:14:07.839
not only that, I want a major harvest of

00:14:04.399 --> 00:14:11.440
souls with my Latinos.

00:14:07.839 --> 00:14:13.600
It's time to bring them in.'I

00:14:11.440 --> 00:14:15.839
want you to pray over President Trump.

00:14:13.600 --> 00:14:19.440
I gave this to you when I saw

00:14:15.839 --> 00:14:22.800
Don Jr. being taken

00:14:19.440 --> 00:14:24.720
out again, and he was no longer here.

00:14:22.800 --> 00:14:27.040
I saw the storm blowing on him,

00:14:24.720 --> 00:14:30.000
and He said, 'It's

00:14:27.040 --> 00:14:32.160
your job. You have to pray for his kids.

00:14:30.000 --> 00:14:35.279
Pray for Don Jr.

00:14:32.160 --> 00:14:38.719
I'm showing you for the fourth time that

00:14:35.279 --> 00:14:42.480
the man's life is in danger.

00:14:38.720 --> 00:14:44.959
Pray for Don Jr.'The other kids

00:14:42.480 --> 00:14:47.120
are not prominent in the vision;

00:14:44.959 --> 00:14:49.760
they're faded. Don Jr. is

00:14:47.120 --> 00:14:51.839
bold and his life is in danger. And the

00:14:49.760 --> 00:14:53.839
Lord said, 'Pray for him. Pray for Don

00:14:51.839 --> 00:14:56.959
Jr.'So,

00:14:53.839 --> 00:14:59.519
instead of opening another package—because

00:14:56.959 --> 00:15:02.560
there's so much more the

00:14:59.519 --> 00:15:05.760
Lord wants to show us—look at what He

00:15:02.560 --> 00:15:08.959
has given me and open the gift

00:15:05.760 --> 00:15:11.360
of a vision, because you don't

00:15:08.959 --> 00:15:13.040
have control over it; Jesus does. It's a

00:15:11.360 --> 00:15:15.360
gift.

00:15:13.040 --> 00:15:17.199
You open it up and don't put the gift

00:15:15.360 --> 00:15:18.959
over here and say, 'Where's my next one?'I

00:15:17.199 --> 00:15:21.199
stopped and I looked and I said,

00:15:18.959 --> 00:15:23.680
'Let's be thankful that He gave us the

00:15:21.199 --> 00:15:26.000
warning ahead of time to pray over Don

00:15:23.680 --> 00:15:28.000
Jr., to pray over the man in Colombia,

00:15:26.000 --> 00:15:29.760
to pray over Cuba, and to pray over

00:15:28.000 --> 00:15:31.839
President Trump to make it across the

00:15:29.760 --> 00:15:33.839
finish line, that he finishes strong,

00:15:31.839 --> 00:15:36.480
that the 25th Amendment does not happen,

00:15:33.839 --> 00:15:39.600
that the Black

00:15:36.480 --> 00:15:41.920
judge in the Supreme Court does not die

00:15:39.600 --> 00:15:44.800
of

00:15:41.920 --> 00:15:47.439
prostate cancer or heart disease,

00:15:44.800 --> 00:15:49.920
that he will stay strong, that

00:15:47.440 --> 00:15:54.040
his life will not be cut off because of

00:15:49.920 --> 00:15:54.040
cancer of the prostate: Clarence

00:15:55.839 --> 00:16:02.399
Thomas.'Pray

00:15:58.240 --> 00:16:05.440
over voices to be accurate.

00:16:02.399 --> 00:16:07.920
Don't criticize; pray for them—the

00:16:05.440 --> 00:16:10.320
prophetic voices, the ones that

00:16:07.920 --> 00:16:12.639
truly have a heart after God and

00:16:10.320 --> 00:16:14.160
are just missing it because they're

00:16:12.639 --> 00:16:15.279
human. Don't go,

00:16:14.160 --> 00:16:16.399
'Well, they're false prophets,'and

00:16:15.279 --> 00:16:19.199
everyone pick

00:16:16.399 --> 00:16:21.759
on people. Instead,

00:16:19.199 --> 00:16:25.519
just see it and go, 'Listen,

00:16:21.759 --> 00:16:27.279
is their heart truly pure and after God

00:16:25.519 --> 00:16:30.959
and they're just off track a little bit?'versus

00:16:27.279 --> 00:16:32.639
if it's malicious.

00:16:30.959 --> 00:16:35.359
There are some people that

00:16:32.639 --> 00:16:37.839
are just good people and just

00:16:35.360 --> 00:16:40.560
need a little fine-tuning. Everybody needs a tuning.

00:16:37.839 --> 00:16:43.519
The rabbit ears get

00:16:40.560 --> 00:16:46.399
fuzzy sometimes because of the cares of life—like

00:16:43.519 --> 00:16:50.240
I told you, the responsibility of

00:16:46.399 --> 00:16:51.600
having fifty staff, 100, or 200 people in your

00:16:50.240 --> 00:16:54.000
church, and you have all this stuff going

00:16:51.600 --> 00:16:55.839
on. You have all this responsibility, and the

00:16:54.000 --> 00:16:57.680
antennas get a little crossed up sometimes

00:16:55.839 --> 00:16:59.440
because you have all the

00:16:57.680 --> 00:17:02.319
cares of life on top of you and

00:16:59.440 --> 00:17:05.439
families depending on you.

00:17:02.320 --> 00:17:08.000
So, in the midst of all the cares

00:17:05.439 --> 00:17:10.400
of life in a huge ministry, from what

00:17:08.000 --> 00:17:10.400
I'm learning,

00:17:10.480 --> 00:17:14.959
have a little grace.

00:17:12.880 --> 00:17:16.959
Pray for some folks; they need help.

00:17:14.959 --> 00:17:19.199
Pray for their finances. Why? We're all

00:17:16.959 --> 00:17:21.439
on the same mission to save that which

00:17:19.199 --> 00:17:23.679
was lost—to tell people that Jesus

00:17:21.439 --> 00:17:26.559
Christ is coming. And some people just

00:17:23.679 --> 00:17:30.080
get a little bit weary in well-doing,

00:17:26.559 --> 00:17:32.799
and they just need some help.

00:17:30.080 --> 00:17:34.639
I would rather reach my hand down to

00:17:32.799 --> 00:17:35.280
a brother in a ditch and pull him out

00:17:34.640 --> 00:17:35.280
than

00:17:35.280 --> 00:17:39.600
throw more dirt on him as I

00:17:36.880 --> 00:17:41.200
walk by.

00:17:39.600 --> 00:17:42.799
There are so many people—the

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:45.679
sister clipboards—who are throwing dirt

00:17:42.799 --> 00:17:48.480
on people right now, and I don't want to

00:17:45.679 --> 00:17:50.640
be associated with it.

00:17:48.480 --> 00:17:52.880
I want to just say, 'Listen, you missed

00:17:50.640 --> 00:17:54.240
it. You messed up. But let's

00:17:52.880 --> 00:17:56.000
pull you out of the ditch.

00:17:54.240 --> 00:17:58.640
Let's look at what you did to help the

00:17:56.000 --> 00:18:01.280
Body of Christ in the past.'Did

00:17:58.640 --> 00:18:03.520
you get people saved? How many did

00:18:01.280 --> 00:18:05.440
you lead to Christ?

00:18:03.520 --> 00:18:08.879
How many people did you help out of the

00:18:05.440 --> 00:18:10.720
ditch whenever they were in the ditch?

00:18:08.880 --> 00:18:12.480
But instead, you didn't throw dirt on

00:18:10.720 --> 00:18:14.960
them. You helped them out and you washed

00:18:12.480 --> 00:18:16.640
them up. You washed their feet. I saw a

00:18:14.960 --> 00:18:21.280
vision

00:18:16.640 --> 00:18:23.600
of Jesus washing the disciples'feet.

00:18:21.280 --> 00:18:26.080
And that was something that we have

00:18:23.600 --> 00:18:28.559
missed as the body of Christ, that we

00:18:26.080 --> 00:18:30.480
don't do that: the washing of the feet.

00:18:28.559 --> 00:18:33.678
This is a sign of covenant. This is

00:18:30.480 --> 00:18:36.559
something more. As I saw

00:18:33.679 --> 00:18:38.640
washing a minister's feet in a vision as

00:18:36.559 --> 00:18:40.399
I was praying, and I saw the individual,

00:18:38.640 --> 00:18:43.520
and the Lord said, 'Do you see the

00:18:40.400 --> 00:18:46.960
washing of the feet?'Jesus was actually

00:18:43.520 --> 00:18:50.799
washing the feet of this person.

00:18:46.960 --> 00:18:52.640
And they were washing his feet.

00:18:50.799 --> 00:18:54.799
And the Lord said, 'There's much

00:18:52.640 --> 00:18:57.520
more to washing of the feet than you

00:18:54.799 --> 00:18:59.600
realize. Not only about humility, but

00:18:57.520 --> 00:19:02.960
there's more to this that I want you to

00:18:59.600 --> 00:19:06.280
pray about that your modern culture

00:19:02.960 --> 00:19:06.280
doesn't get.

00:19:06.400 --> 00:19:11.760
Washing of the feet. Jesus

00:19:09.440 --> 00:19:13.600
washed their feet.'And the Lord was

00:19:11.760 --> 00:19:16.400
speaking to me about washing of the feet today—well,

00:19:13.600 --> 00:19:18.399
actually yesterday, it was

00:19:16.400 --> 00:19:21.039
last

00:19:18.400 --> 00:19:23.440
night. And I was praying into that

00:19:21.039 --> 00:19:25.679
washing of the feet. There's more to

00:19:23.440 --> 00:19:27.919
this. And I thought, what is more to

00:19:25.679 --> 00:19:30.080
washing of the feet? Jesus took

00:19:27.919 --> 00:19:32.400
Communion and he washed their feet. I

00:19:30.080 --> 00:19:35.120
thought, why?

00:19:32.400 --> 00:19:37.840
There's more to this.

00:19:35.120 --> 00:19:40.080
I know in my modern thinking, it's just

00:19:37.840 --> 00:19:42.559
like, what really is that? I

00:19:40.080 --> 00:19:45.918
mean, I hate to be

00:19:42.559 --> 00:19:48.918
ignorant, sorry, but I was just like,

00:19:49.679 --> 00:19:56.720
'Lord, you can't wash my feet.'But

00:19:53.760 --> 00:19:59.520
even Peter and them, they were

00:19:56.720 --> 00:20:01.760
freaking out about it. But Jesus

00:19:59.520 --> 00:20:03.918
humbled himself and he washed their feet,

00:20:01.760 --> 00:20:05.679
and they washed his feet.

00:20:03.919 --> 00:20:09.200
It was a covenant. There's

00:20:05.679 --> 00:20:10.960
something more to it.

00:20:09.200 --> 00:20:12.400
And I'm sure somebody's written

00:20:10.960 --> 00:20:14.000
some book about it and they feel like

00:20:12.400 --> 00:20:15.919
they're an expert at it. But the Lord

00:20:14.000 --> 00:20:19.480
said there's a deeper revelation

00:20:15.919 --> 00:20:19.480
than what you realize.

00:20:21.120 --> 00:20:29.840
And I thought, well, I want to be a

00:20:23.440 --> 00:20:32.159
student. Show me. I'll wash your feet,

00:20:29.840 --> 00:20:35.720
Lord. I'll wash the

00:20:32.159 --> 00:20:35.720
minister's feet.

00:20:35.840 --> 00:20:39.879
There's something about it.

00:20:40.880 --> 00:20:47.600
So, that's where I was at today. I'm just

00:20:42.559 --> 00:20:51.520
telling you, I think it's easy to

00:20:47.600 --> 00:20:53.918
be a critic. It's easy to always poke.

00:20:51.520 --> 00:20:56.720
It's easy to always think, 'Well,

00:20:53.919 --> 00:20:59.120
my life's not that way.'Whenever

00:20:56.720 --> 00:21:00.960
you realize when I talk, we

00:20:59.120 --> 00:21:02.639
go over Kathryn Kuhlman's life and her

00:21:00.960 --> 00:21:06.159
autobiography,

00:21:02.640 --> 00:21:08.480
reading over her struggles and

00:21:06.159 --> 00:21:12.480
her trials and how really

00:21:08.480 --> 00:21:15.280
beautiful a person she was.

00:21:12.480 --> 00:21:18.080
She had issues. We all have issues. But

00:21:15.280 --> 00:21:22.799
she truly was a beautiful soul. She was

00:21:18.080 --> 00:21:25.918
a beautiful person. And

00:21:22.799 --> 00:21:28.400
I just want to be more like Jesus.

00:21:25.919 --> 00:21:31.039
And the more I get into

00:21:28.400 --> 00:21:33.120
ministry and the more I've learned, it

00:21:31.039 --> 00:21:35.520
pulls you more away from him, the more

00:21:33.120 --> 00:21:38.000
they draw you to him because of the

00:21:35.520 --> 00:21:39.918
pressures of things.

00:21:38.000 --> 00:21:41.840
And the more I realized the Lord said,

00:21:39.919 --> 00:21:44.320
'What is it you need of, Brandon? What

00:21:41.840 --> 00:21:45.760
is this that I've shown

00:21:44.320 --> 00:21:48.240
you? I've done it.'And I thought,

00:21:48.240 --> 00:21:54.640
'Lord, if it all goes away, you provided

00:21:51.200 --> 00:21:57.919
everything. You gave me

00:21:54.640 --> 00:21:59.919
all these lights, the camera, the talk.

00:21:57.919 --> 00:22:04.280
You did it all.

00:21:59.919 --> 00:22:04.280
And I said what you told me to say.'So

00:22:04.960 --> 00:22:08.640
I don't know. It was

00:22:06.960 --> 00:22:11.520
interesting today. I don't know if

00:22:08.640 --> 00:22:13.520
that helps you any, but it helped me.

00:22:11.520 --> 00:22:16.559
And I think for people who are

00:22:13.520 --> 00:22:18.080
trying really hard to do ministry and

00:22:16.559 --> 00:22:20.399
you see the Candace Owens, you see the

00:22:18.080 --> 00:22:22.480
Tuckers, and I told you

00:22:20.400 --> 00:22:24.480
there's going to be a great criticism

00:22:22.480 --> 00:22:27.840
coming out of people in the days ahead

00:22:24.480 --> 00:22:29.679
concerning the Christians, concerning

00:22:27.840 --> 00:22:32.799
the way we believe. There are things

00:22:29.679 --> 00:22:34.400
that are going to be criticized greatly.

00:22:32.799 --> 00:22:36.080
And we haven't seen the beginning of

00:22:34.400 --> 00:22:38.640
persecution that's coming to the church

00:22:36.080 --> 00:22:41.840
in America.

00:22:38.640 --> 00:22:45.200
There's great persecution coming.

00:22:41.840 --> 00:22:46.959
And I've seen some very hard things.

00:22:45.200 --> 00:22:49.600
But I know that in the midst of

00:22:46.960 --> 00:22:51.600
persecution, it brings forth the

00:22:49.600 --> 00:22:54.879
greater glory. The greater the

00:22:51.600 --> 00:22:58.158
persecution, the greater the glory.

00:22:54.880 --> 00:23:01.600
Trials bring forth glory. The refining

00:22:58.159 --> 00:23:03.919
brings forth the glory.

00:23:01.600 --> 00:23:08.039
So, all right. There you go. How long

00:23:03.919 --> 00:23:08.039
was that? Oh, 35 minutes.

00:23:09.520 --> 00:23:12.559
Okay. Do you want to show them anything

00:23:10.880 --> 00:23:13.440
in the news?

00:23:13.440 --> 00:23:18.880
I'm trying to

00:23:15.840 --> 00:23:20.559
break myself of calling you 'babe'.

00:23:20.559 --> 00:23:23.799
Go ahead.

00:23:24.159 --> 00:23:27.200
Okay.

00:23:27.200 --> 00:23:30.960
Turkey had a meeting with Poland today.

00:23:29.360 --> 00:23:33.840
Now, what did we say was going to

00:23:30.960 --> 00:23:35.520
happen? I said the Lord said Turkey

00:23:33.840 --> 00:23:38.000
would rise up and it would be about

00:23:35.520 --> 00:23:39.760
Warsaw, Poland, and they'll strike

00:23:38.000 --> 00:23:42.760
Poland in the days ahead. This is

00:23:39.760 --> 00:23:42.760
interesting.

00:23:43.520 --> 00:23:46.879
Why did Turkey meet Poland today?

00:23:45.360 --> 00:23:50.080
They did a prayer for him.

00:23:46.880 --> 00:23:52.080
Yeah, they did a prayer.

00:23:50.080 --> 00:23:52.879
Well, that's interesting. Is that in

00:23:52.080 --> 00:23:54.158
Turkey?

00:23:52.880 --> 00:23:58.520
No, this is in Turkey.

00:23:54.159 --> 00:23:58.520
Wow. That's what Turkey looks like.

00:23:58.720 --> 00:24:01.600
So Poland came to Turkey.

00:24:00.799 --> 00:24:03.440
Yes.

00:24:01.600 --> 00:24:05.600
That's interesting. So Turkey's really

00:24:03.440 --> 00:24:06.880
pretty.

00:24:05.600 --> 00:24:08.559
That's not what I thought it would look

00:24:06.880 --> 00:24:12.280
like;

00:24:08.559 --> 00:24:12.280
I thought it'd be rocky.

00:24:21.919 --> 00:24:24.919
Yeah.

00:24:25.600 --> 00:24:31.918
The vampire is really stretching out

00:24:28.640 --> 00:24:33.760
today for sure.

00:24:31.919 --> 00:24:35.200
Yeah. So, he had him over and

00:24:33.760 --> 00:24:36.480
they were talking. I was trying to

00:24:35.200 --> 00:24:39.679
recapture and see what they were saying,

00:24:36.480 --> 00:24:41.279
but there's not very many.

00:24:42.640 --> 00:24:45.279
What was their point?

00:24:43.919 --> 00:24:46.640
What was the point of going there?

00:24:45.279 --> 00:24:49.039
I don't know. I think it was

00:24:46.640 --> 00:24:50.880
because Ukraine was trying to

00:24:49.039 --> 00:24:54.072
strike them.

00:24:50.880 --> 00:24:54.080
So, they're trying to...

